    "name": "The Last Viking",
    "steam_appid": 3142500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142500/extras/932b402edd529f99341405477e62ecdf.avif?t=1764065697\" width=616 height=130 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142500/extras/0087efd7f161b64baf36a24774c7bc9d.avif?t=1764065697\" width=616 height=130 /></span><br>《最后的维京人》是一款沉浸式多人合作生存游戏。你将扮演一名年轻的维京战士，在孤岛上进行生存、探索和发现的冒险。你被困在一个充满秘密和危险的孤岛上，必须运用你的技能在恶劣的环境中生存。参与史诗般的战斗，打造强大的工具，并发现古老的秘密，以实现你的命运。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索世界并生存</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142500/extras/20c371af00d4319320dfb596f82d14cc.poster.avif?t=1764065697\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142500/extras/20c371af00d4319320dfb596f82d14cc.webm?t=1764065697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>沉浸在一个美丽设计的世界中，在这里生存是你的主要目标。你探索的岛屿充满生机并笼罩在神秘中。管理你的饥饿、口渴、睡眠，并警惕天气变化。岛上的每个角落都隐藏着能帮助你完成任务的秘密。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与敌人战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142500/extras/794048eb4f14e7cebc76d589a06758f9.poster.avif?t=1764065697\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142500/extras/794048eb4f14e7cebc76d589a06758f9.webm?t=1764065697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>与凶猛的野兽、骷髅和神话生物进行激烈的战斗。掌握你的武器，精进战斗技巧，以应对岛上最致命的敌人。参与与传奇生物的刺激Boss战，每个Boss都带来独特的挑战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造和制作</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142500/extras/6e25de9a2e19e11cf5c5671ed37772e6.poster.avif?t=1764065697\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142500/extras/6e25de9a2e19e11cf5c5671ed37772e6.webm?t=1764065697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>通过制作必需的工具和建造重要的庇护所，铺平你的生存之路。从环境中收集资源，发现帮助你制作一切的配方，从简单的武器到强大的维京装备。建造建筑来保护自己免受自然的侵袭，并升级你的武器库以应对危险。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与朋友一起游戏</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142500/extras/ff84404e3977d9585f12a73e9af424e5.poster.avif?t=1764065697\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142500/extras/ff84404e3977d9585f12a73e9af424e5.webm?t=1764065697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>体验《最后的维京人》的合作多人模式，最多可容纳8名玩家，共同在岛上生存和征服。与朋友分享资源，策划战斗策略，并一起建造维京村落。",
